{"tid":844612,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[HK Have IT!] 江嘉敏秘撻電競男 闢私竇煙韌","createTime":"2018-10-02T04:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T09:16:28.000Z","uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"194bfd662388d87d48ad066e110e0e243c969afd","tid":844612,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/02/udhCD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2FudhCD0.jpg&h=b359d6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/02/9p8L2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F9p8L2O.jpg&h=e40c97d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/02/MZoNvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2FMZoNvR.jpg&h=5df7dc32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/02/WZi0SJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2FWZi0SJ.jpg&h=b4a28ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/02/HCaiRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2FHCaiRt.jpg&h=ce9a339d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宅男咪神江嘉敏形象清純，早前仍表示單身的她原來已秘密開「Dry」，戀上一名年約30歲的電競公司高層Anthony！兩人拍拖以來極為鬼祟，還在西貢闢私竇密室培情，連日來共度春宵，嘴角含春的江嘉敏還情不自禁與男友十指緊扣，不過好事被撞破時，即包到冚速逃！<br />\n現年23歲的江嘉敏去年在劇集《親親我好媽》憑「學生Look」獲宅男盛讚純過蒸餾水，被視為「宅男咪神」隨即上位劇接劇，緋聞亦一大籮，曾被指與王浩信拍攝《兄弟》時做「小三」主動獻殷勤，又私下與對方傳短訊。雖然緋聞多多，但她不時表示仍然單身，原來近月已封盤，暗撻身高六呎的Anthony，男友更是著名電競公司高層，家住太子道西價值千多萬港元的豪宅，平時駕駛寶馬房車出入。"},{"pid":"3fe35aab23912f49697df7002015214e1bf7f6d5","tid":844612,"uid":211976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911bd8e5483084ff94fdad3bc2d31d7286823c70","tid":844612,"uid":181905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/122048_9eaed7cef432d293fef8bea8a987b68a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F122048_9eaed7cef432d293fef8bea8a987b68a.gif&h=31278a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d62585a22029a1a429266860fa599e85abccdc25","tid":844612,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"俾王浩信玩完就搵有錢仔賣單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5df58f1f8e913a53006916093923bf9799b621","tid":844612,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"成個呀嬸樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}